task.summary: Add fontawesome and bootstrap as npm packages
Rename all places with image to photo for consistency
Refactor photostore to manage actions for photos
Add prop to identify if photo is selected to store so that thumbnail does not need to have logic
Add random functionality. If random number is already the photo we continue trying to generate next random
Move harcoded actions to actions constant.
Implement store, reducers and actions to achieve the "redux-way"
Refactor code to update container component
Test that dispatch is called with load as index is loaded

Add snapshot test for photo navigation.
In order to have a reliable test including random button I had to refactor random gneration to separate module and mock it in the test to always return the same thing.
